import { Component, OnInit } from '@angular/core'; import { LoguearService } from '../../service/loguear.service'; import { ExamenService } from 'src/app/admin/services/examen.service'; import { Router } from '@angular/router'; @Component({ selector: 'app-home', templateUrl: './home.component.html', styleUrls: ['./home.component.css'] }) export class HomeComponent implements OnInit { loggg : boolean = false salir : boolean = false listExamn : any; AdminFijo = localStorage.getItem('role') constructor(private loginName:LoguearService,private obtenerNombre:ExamenService,private router:Router) { } ngOnInit(): void { if(localStorage.getItem("islogeado")== null) //this.loginName.getOrganizacionId().subscribe( //(data) => {this.loggg= data,console.log("fijero adentro")} ) this.obtenerNombre.getExam().subscribe( (data)=> {this.listExamn=data} ) } Salir(){ localStorage.clear() this.router.navigate(['/auth/login']) } }
